snippet.title: Guns N' Roses - Don't Cry (Cover)
snippet.description:
Siegfried Song Facebook :
http://www.facebook.com/SiegfriedSongOfficial
David Olivares Facebook : 
https://www.facebook.com/DavidOlivaresQ
Jotun Studio :
http://www.jotunstudio.es

This is a collaboration cover of Don't Cry with David Olivares. It's little bit more aggressive than the original version and it's been also my intention to make this cover an individual thing and not a direct copy of the original vocals. It's up to you to decide whether the attempt has been successful or not.

If you like this song, please visit my facebook page.
Thank You.

David Olivares - All Instruments and arrangement
Siegfried Song - Lead and harmony Vocals
Leo Peńa at Jotun Studio - mix, edit and master
